Filmstrip: **5–8 blank frames** before content — server HTML + blocking CSS, not empty AJAX sliders.

## Root causes (confirmed in code)

1. **TTFB / document latency** — `#1 bottleneck`
   - `offers_sliders.php` + `load-cpt-slider.php`: full SSR of all bachelor/master slides
   - `product-slide.php`: multiple `get_field()`, `get_the_terms()`, `wp_get_post_terms()` per slide (no `akademiata_get_offer_terms` yet)
   - `front-page.php`: `get_fields()`, hero, YouTube SSR, news `WP_Query`, WPML

2. **Render blocking** — `configure/js-css.php`: Bootstrap 4 CDN CSS, `main.css` (~364 KB), Adobe Typekit; `header.php`: GTM/gtag on prod after `wp_head`

3. **Mobile TBT** — global `vendors.js` (~455 KB) + `main.js` (~98 KB) + jQuery + Bootstrap/Popper CDN on every page; webpack `splitChunks` puts slick/swiper/fancyapps/vimeo in shared `vendors.js` even where unused

4. **Images** — slider `background-image` without lazy strategy; hero has `akademiata_preload_main_slider_image` (OK for LCP)

## Do NOT break

- Offer listing SSR + prefetch (`page-offer.php`, `ajax-filter.js`, `ajax_filters.php`)
- PG/MBA separate flow
- Cookiebot (WP plugin only — do not duplicate in theme)
- GTM on prod without user/marketing approval
- Bootstrap CDN vs npm BS5 — audit before removing either (BS4 CDN + BS5 in bundle coexist)

## Implementation plan (in order)

### Phase 0 — Hosting (no theme code, highest TTFB win)

- [ ] Page cache on prod (LiteSpeed Cache / WP Rocket) for homepage
- [ ] Object cache (Redis) if available
- [ ] Long cache headers on `assets/dist/`
- [ ] HTTP/2 or HTTP/3 on server

### Phase 1 — Low-risk theme (start here if no hosting access)

- [ ] `product-slide.php`: use `akademiata_get_offer_terms()` (like `card_post.php`)
- [ ] Transient cache HTML of `offers_sliders` fragment (per WPML lang, ~1 h); invalidate on bachelor/master save if feasible
- [ ] `preconnect` in `header.php` or `js-css.php`: `cdn.jsdelivr.net`, `use.typekit.net`
- [ ] Typekit kit: `font-display: swap` in Adobe project settings

### Phase 2 — Homepage sliders hybrid (medium risk, big TTFB win)

Same pattern as offer listings (`23bf7a4`):

- [ ] SSR first **12–16** visible Slick slides per CPT
- [ ] Background AJAX for rest + Slick init/refresh (`ajax-load-cpt.js`, `load-cpt-slider.php`)
- [ ] Do **not** return to empty slider containers

### Phase 3 — JS split (medium risk, mobile TBT)

- [ ] Webpack: slick/swiper not in global `vendors.js` on non-slider pages
- [ ] Dynamic import in `_generalScripts.js` for video/YouTube/fancybox where possible
- [ ] Audit duplicate Bootstrap 4 CDN vs npm BS5

### Phase 4 — Only with explicit approval

- [ ] Defer GTM/gtag load
- [ ] Critical CSS inline

